title: You're Still Going To Get There | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: You're Still Going To Get There | Joel Osteen
description:
No setback is big enough to derail your destiny. Storms may come, but God is still in control of the winds.

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
